{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I heard this amazing story about Miuccia Prada."},{"time":3000,"text":"She's an Italian fashion designer."},{"time":5000,"text":"She goes to this vintage store in Paris"},{"time":7000,"text":"with a friend of hers."},{"time":9000,"text":"She's rooting around, she finds this one jacket by Balenciaga --"},{"time":13000,"text":"she loves it."},{"time":15000,"text":"She's turning it inside out."},{"time":17000,"text":"She's looking at the seams. She's looking at the construction."},{"time":20000,"text":"Her friend says, \"Buy it already.\""},{"time":22000,"text":"She said, \"I'll buy it, but I'm also going to replicate it.\""},{"time":27000,"text":"Now, the academics in this audience may think,"},{"time":30000,"text":"\"Well, that sounds like plagiarism.\""},{"time":32000,"text":"But to a fashionista, what it really is"},{"time":34000,"text":"is a sign of Prada's genius:"},{"time":36000,"text":"that she can root through the history of fashion"},{"time":38000,"text":"and pick the one jacket"},{"time":40000,"text":"that doesn't need to be changed by one iota,"},{"time":42000,"text":"and to be current and to be now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45000,"text":"You might also be asking whether it's possible"},{"time":48000,"text":"that this is illegal for her to do this."},{"time":51000,"text":"Well, it turns out that it's actually not illegal."},{"time":54000,"text":"In the fashion industry, there's very little"},{"time":56000,"text":"intellectual property protection."},{"time":59000,"text":"They have trademark protection,"},{"time":61000,"text":"but no copyright protection"},{"time":63000,"text":"and no patent protection to speak of."},{"time":66000,"text":"All they have, really, is trademark protection,"},{"time":68000,"text":"and so it means that anybody"},{"time":70000,"text":"could copy any garment"},{"time":72000,"text":"on any person in this room"},{"time":74000,"text":"and sell it as their own design."},{"time":76000,"text":"The only thing that they can't copy"},{"time":78000,"text":"is the actual trademark label"},{"time":80000,"text":"within that piece of apparel."},{"time":82000,"text":"That's one reason that you see logos"},{"time":84000,"text":"splattered all over these products."},{"time":86000,"text":"It's because it's a lot harder for knock-off artists"},{"time":88000,"text":"to knock off these designs"},{"time":90000,"text":"because they can't knock off the logo."},{"time":93000,"text":"But if you go to Santee Alley, yeah."},{"time":96000,"text":"(Laughter) Well, yeah."},{"time":98000,"text":"Canal Street, I know."},{"time":100000,"text":"And sometimes these are fun, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"Now, the reason for this, the reason that the fashion industry"},{"time":105000,"text":"doesn't have any copyright protection"},{"time":107000,"text":"is because the courts decided long ago"},{"time":110000,"text":"that apparel is too utilitarian"},{"time":112000,"text":"to qualify for copyright protection."},{"time":114000,"text":"They didn't want a handful of designers"},{"time":116000,"text":"owning the seminal building blocks of our clothing."},{"time":119000,"text":"And then everybody else would have to license this cuff or this sleeve"},{"time":122000,"text":"because Joe Blow owns it."},{"time":126000,"text":"But too utilitarian? I mean is that the way you think of fashion?"},{"time":129000,"text":"This is Vivienne Westwood. No!"},{"time":132000,"text":"We think of it as maybe too silly,"},{"time":134000,"text":"too unnecessary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136000,"text":"Now, those of you who are familiar with the logic"},{"time":138000,"text":"behind copyright protection --"},{"time":140000,"text":"which is that without ownership, there is no incentive to innovate --"},{"time":143000,"text":"might be really surprised"},{"time":145000,"text":"by both the critical success of the fashion industry"},{"time":148000,"text":"and the economic success of this industry."},{"time":151000,"text":"What I'm going to argue today is that"},{"time":153000,"text":"because there's no copyright protection"},{"time":155000,"text":"in the fashion industry,"},{"time":157000,"text":"fashion designers have actually been able to elevate"},{"time":160000,"text":"utilitarian design,"},{"time":162000,"text":"things to cover our naked bodies,"},{"time":164000,"text":"into something that we consider art."},{"time":166000,"text":"Because there's no copyright protection"},{"time":168000,"text":"in this industry,"},{"time":170000,"text":"there's a very open and creative"},{"time":172000,"text":"ecology of creativity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174000,"text":"Unlike their creative brothers and sisters,"},{"time":176000,"text":"who are sculptors or photographers"},{"time":179000,"text":"or filmmakers or musicians,"},{"time":182000,"text":"fashion designers can sample"},{"time":184000,"text":"from all their peers' designs."},{"time":186000,"text":"They can take any element from any garment"},{"time":188000,"text":"from the history of fashion"},{"time":190000,"text":"and incorporate it into their own design."},{"time":192000,"text":"They're also notorious for riffing off of the zeitgeist."},{"time":195000,"text":"And here, I suspect,"},{"time":197000,"text":"they were influenced by the costumes in Avatar."},{"time":200000,"text":"Maybe just a little."},{"time":202000,"text":"Can't copyright a costume either."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204000,"text":"Now, fashion designers have"},{"time":206000,"text":"the broadest palette imaginable"},{"time":208000,"text":"in this creative industry."},{"time":210000,"text":"This wedding dress here"},{"time":212000,"text":"is actually made of sporks,"},{"time":215000,"text":"and this dress is actually made of aluminum."},{"time":218000,"text":"I've heard this dress actually sort of sounds like wind chimes"},{"time":220000,"text":"as they walk through."},{"time":222000,"text":"So, one of the magical side effects"},{"time":224000,"text":"of having a culture of copying,"},{"time":226000,"text":"which is really what it is,"},{"time":228000,"text":"is the establishment of trends."},{"time":230000,"text":"People think this is a magical thing. How does it happen?"},{"time":232000,"text":"Well, it's because it's legal for people to copy one another."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235000,"text":"Some people believe that"},{"time":237000,"text":"there are a few people at the top of the fashion food chain"},{"time":240000,"text":"who sort of dictate to us what we're all going to wear,"},{"time":243000,"text":"but if you talk to any designer at any level,"},{"time":245000,"text":"including these high-end designers,"},{"time":247000,"text":"they always say"},{"time":249000,"text":"their main inspiration comes from the street:"},{"time":251000,"text":"where people like you and me remix and match"},{"time":253000,"text":"our own fashion looks."},{"time":255000,"text":"And that's where they really get a lot of their"},{"time":257000,"text":"creative inspiration,"},{"time":260000,"text":"so it's both a top-down and a bottom-up kind of industry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264000,"text":"Now, the fast fashion giants have"},{"time":266000,"text":"probably benefited the most"},{"time":268000,"text":"from the lack of copyright protection in the fashion industry."},{"time":271000,"text":"They are notorious for knocking off high-end designs"},{"time":274000,"text":"and selling them at very low prices."},{"time":276000,"text":"And they've been faced with a lot of lawsuits,"},{"time":279000,"text":"but those lawsuits are usually not won by fashion designers."},{"time":282000,"text":"The courts have said over and over again, \"You don't need"},{"time":284000,"text":"any more intellectual property protection.\""},{"time":287000,"text":"When you look at copies like this,"},{"time":290000,"text":"you wonder: How do the luxury high-end brands"},{"time":292000,"text":"remain in business?"},{"time":294000,"text":"If you can get it for 200 bucks, why pay a thousand?"},{"time":297000,"text":"Well, that's one reason we had a conference here at USC a few years ago."},{"time":300000,"text":"We invited Tom Ford to come --"},{"time":302000,"text":"the conference was called, \"Ready to Share:"},{"time":304000,"text":"Fashion and the Ownership of Creativity\" --"},{"time":307000,"text":"and we asked him exactly this question."},{"time":309000,"text":"Here's what he had to say."},{"time":311000,"text":"He had just come off a successful stint as the lead designer at Gucci,"},{"time":314000,"text":"in case you didn't know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":316000,"text":"Tom Ford: And we found after much research"},{"time":319000,"text":"that -- actually not much research, quite simple research --"},{"time":321000,"text":"that the counterfeit customer was not our customer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324000,"text":"Johanna Blakley: Imagine that."},{"time":326000,"text":"The people on Santee Alley"},{"time":328000,"text":"are not the ones who shop at Gucci."},{"time":330000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":333000,"text":"This is a very different demographic."},{"time":337000,"text":"And, you know, a knock-off is never the same"},{"time":340000,"text":"as an original high-end design,"},{"time":343000,"text":"at least in terms of the materials; they're always made of cheaper materials."},{"time":346000,"text":"But even sometimes a cheaper version"},{"time":349000,"text":"can actually have some charming aspects,"},{"time":351000,"text":"can breathe a little extra life into a dying trend."},{"time":355000,"text":"There's lots of virtues of copying."},{"time":357000,"text":"One that a lot of cultural critics have pointed to"},{"time":360000,"text":"is that we now have"},{"time":362000,"text":"a much broader palette"},{"time":364000,"text":"of design choices to choose from than we ever have before,"},{"time":367000,"text":"and this is mainly because of the fast fashion industry, actually."},{"time":370000,"text":"And this is a good thing. We need lots of options."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372000,"text":"Fashion, whether you like it or not,"},{"time":374000,"text":"helps you project who you are to the world."},{"time":378000,"text":"Because of fast fashion,"},{"time":380000,"text":"global trends actually get established much more quickly than they used to."},{"time":383000,"text":"And this, actually, is good news to trendsetters;"},{"time":386000,"text":"they want trends to be set"},{"time":388000,"text":"so that they can move product."},{"time":391000,"text":"For fashionistas,"},{"time":393000,"text":"they want to stay ahead of the curve."},{"time":395000,"text":"They don't want to be wearing what everybody else is wearing."},{"time":398000,"text":"And so, they want to move on to the next trend"},{"time":401000,"text":"as soon as possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403000,"text":"I tell you, there is no rest for the fashionable."},{"time":406000,"text":"Every season, these designers have to struggle"},{"time":408000,"text":"to come up with the new fabulous idea that everybody's going to love."},{"time":411000,"text":"And this, let me tell you,"},{"time":413000,"text":"is very good for the bottom line."},{"time":416000,"text":"Now of course, there's a bunch of effects"},{"time":418000,"text":"that this culture of copying has"},{"time":420000,"text":"on the creative process."},{"time":422000,"text":"And Stuart Weitzman is a very successful shoe designer."},{"time":424000,"text":"He has complained a lot about people copying him,"},{"time":427000,"text":"but in one interview I read,"},{"time":429000,"text":"he said it has really forced him to up his game."},{"time":432000,"text":"He had to come up with new ideas,"},{"time":434000,"text":"new things that would be hard to copy."},{"time":436000,"text":"He came up with this Bowden-wedge heel"},{"time":439000,"text":"that has to be made out of steel or titanium;"},{"time":441000,"text":"if you make it from some sort of cheaper material,"},{"time":443000,"text":"it'll actually crack in two."},{"time":445000,"text":"It forced him to be a little more innovative. (Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":448000,"text":"And that actually reminded me"},{"time":450000,"text":"of jazz great, Charlie Parker."},{"time":452000,"text":"I don't know if you've heard this anecdote, but I have."},{"time":455000,"text":"He said that one of the reasons he invented bebop"},{"time":458000,"text":"was that he was pretty sure"},{"time":460000,"text":"that white musicians wouldn't be able to replicate the sound. (Laughter)"},{"time":466000,"text":"He wanted to make it too difficult to copy,"},{"time":470000,"text":"and that's what fashion designers are doing all the time."},{"time":472000,"text":"They're trying to put together"},{"time":474000,"text":"a signature look, an aesthetic"},{"time":476000,"text":"that reflects who they are."},{"time":478000,"text":"When people knock it off, everybody knows"},{"time":481000,"text":"because they've put that look out on the runway,"},{"time":483000,"text":"and it's a coherent aesthetic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":487000,"text":"I love these Gallianos."},{"time":489000,"text":"Okay, we'll move on. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":491000,"text":"This is not unlike the world of comedy."},{"time":494000,"text":"I don't know if you know that jokes"},{"time":496000,"text":"also can't be copyright protected."},{"time":498000,"text":"So when one-liners were really popular,"},{"time":501000,"text":"everybody stole them from one another."},{"time":503000,"text":"But now, we have a different kind of comic."},{"time":505000,"text":"They develop a persona,"},{"time":507000,"text":"a signature style, much like fashion designers."},{"time":510000,"text":"And their jokes,"},{"time":512000,"text":"much like the fashion designs by a fashion designer,"},{"time":514000,"text":"really only work within that aesthetic."},{"time":516000,"text":"If somebody steals a joke"},{"time":518000,"text":"from Larry David, for instance,"},{"time":520000,"text":"it's not as funny."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522000,"text":"Now, the other thing that fashion designers have done"},{"time":524000,"text":"to survive in this culture of copying"},{"time":526000,"text":"is they've learned how to copy themselves."},{"time":528000,"text":"They knock themselves off."},{"time":530000,"text":"They make deals with the fast fashion giants"},{"time":533000,"text":"and they come up with a way to sell their product"},{"time":535000,"text":"to a whole new demographic:"},{"time":537000,"text":"the Santee Alley demographic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":539000,"text":"Now, some fashion designers will say,"},{"time":542000,"text":"\"It's only in the United States that we don't have any respect."},{"time":545000,"text":"In other countries there is protection"},{"time":547000,"text":"for our artful designs.\""},{"time":550000,"text":"But if you take a look at the two other biggest markets in the world,"},{"time":552000,"text":"it turns out that the protection that's offered"},{"time":555000,"text":"is really ineffectual."},{"time":557000,"text":"In Japan, for instance, which I think is the third largest market,"},{"time":560000,"text":"they have a design law; it protects apparel,"},{"time":563000,"text":"but the novelty standard is so high,"},{"time":565000,"text":"you have to prove that your garment has never existed before,"},{"time":568000,"text":"it's totally unique."},{"time":570000,"text":"And that's sort of like"},{"time":572000,"text":"the novelty standard for a U.S. patent,"},{"time":574000,"text":"which fashion designers never get --"},{"time":576000,"text":"rarely get here in the states."}]},{"cues":[{"time":578000,"text":"In the European Union, they went in the other direction."},{"time":581000,"text":"Very low novelty standard,"},{"time":583000,"text":"anybody can register anything."},{"time":585000,"text":"But even though it's the home of the fast fashion industry"},{"time":587000,"text":"and you have a lot of luxury designers there,"},{"time":589000,"text":"they don't register their garments, generally,"},{"time":592000,"text":"and there's not a lot of litigation."},{"time":594000,"text":"It turns out it's because the novelty standard is too low."},{"time":597000,"text":"A person can come in and take somebody else's gown,"},{"time":600000,"text":"cut off three inches from the bottom,"},{"time":603000,"text":"go to the E.U. and register it as a new, original design."},{"time":606000,"text":"So, that does not stop the knock-off artists."},{"time":608000,"text":"If you look at the registry, actually,"},{"time":610000,"text":"a lot of the registered things in the E.U."},{"time":612000,"text":"are Nike T-shirts"},{"time":614000,"text":"that are almost identical to one another."}]},{"cues":[{"time":617000,"text":"But this has not stopped Diane von Furstenberg."},{"time":619000,"text":"She is the head of"},{"time":621000,"text":"the Council of Fashion Designers of America,"},{"time":624000,"text":"and she has told her constituency that"},{"time":626000,"text":"she is going to get copyright protection"},{"time":629000,"text":"for fashion designs."},{"time":631000,"text":"The retailers have kind of quashed this notion though."},{"time":633000,"text":"I don't think the legislation is going anywhere,"},{"time":635000,"text":"because they realized it is so hard"},{"time":638000,"text":"to tell the difference between a pirated design"},{"time":640000,"text":"and something that's just part of a global trend."},{"time":643000,"text":"Who owns a look?"},{"time":645000,"text":"That is a very difficult question to answer."},{"time":647000,"text":"It takes lots of lawyers and lots of court time,"},{"time":650000,"text":"and the retailers decided that would be way too expensive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":655000,"text":"You know, it's not just the fashion industry"},{"time":657000,"text":"that doesn't have copyright protection."},{"time":659000,"text":"There's a bunch of other industries that don't have copyright protection,"},{"time":662000,"text":"including the food industry."},{"time":664000,"text":"You cannot copyright a recipe"},{"time":666000,"text":"because it's a set of instructions, it's fact,"},{"time":669000,"text":"and you cannot copyright the look and feel"},{"time":671000,"text":"of even the most unique dish."},{"time":674000,"text":"Same with automobiles."},{"time":676000,"text":"It doesn't matter how wacky they look or how cool they look,"},{"time":679000,"text":"you cannot copyright the sculptural design."},{"time":682000,"text":"It's a utilitarian article, that's why."},{"time":685000,"text":"Same with furniture,"},{"time":687000,"text":"it's too utilitarian."},{"time":690000,"text":"Magic tricks, I think they're instructions, sort of like recipes:"},{"time":693000,"text":"no copyright protection."},{"time":695000,"text":"Hairdos, no copyright protection."},{"time":697000,"text":"Open source software, these guys decided"},{"time":699000,"text":"they didn't want copyright protection."},{"time":701000,"text":"They thought it'd be more innovative without it."},{"time":704000,"text":"It's really hard to get copyright for databases."},{"time":707000,"text":"Tattoo artists, they don't want it; it's not cool."},{"time":710000,"text":"They share their designs."},{"time":713000,"text":"Jokes, no copyright protection."},{"time":715000,"text":"Fireworks displays,"},{"time":717000,"text":"the rules of games,"},{"time":719000,"text":"the smell of perfume: no."},{"time":722000,"text":"And some of these industries may seem"},{"time":724000,"text":"sort of marginal to you,"},{"time":726000,"text":"but these are the gross sales"},{"time":729000,"text":"for low I.P. industries,"},{"time":731000,"text":"industries with very little copyright protection,"},{"time":733000,"text":"and there's the gross sales of"},{"time":735000,"text":"films and books."},{"time":737000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":740000,"text":"It ain't pretty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":742000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":744000,"text":"So you talk to people in the fashion industry"},{"time":746000,"text":"and they're like, \"Shhh!"},{"time":748000,"text":"Don't tell anybody"},{"time":750000,"text":"we can actually steal from each other's designs."},{"time":752000,"text":"It's embarrassing.\""},{"time":754000,"text":"But you know what? It's revolutionary,"},{"time":756000,"text":"and it's a model that a lot of other industries --"},{"time":759000,"text":"like the ones we just saw with the really small bars --"},{"time":762000,"text":"they might have to think about this."},{"time":764000,"text":"Because right now, those industries with a lot of copyright protection"},{"time":767000,"text":"are operating in an atmosphere"},{"time":769000,"text":"where it's as if they don't have any protection,"},{"time":772000,"text":"and they don't know what to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":776000,"text":"When I found out that there are a whole bunch of industries"},{"time":779000,"text":"that didn't have copyright protection,"},{"time":781000,"text":"I thought, \"What exactly is the underlying logic?"},{"time":784000,"text":"I want a picture.\" And the lawyers do not provide a picture,"},{"time":787000,"text":"so I made one."},{"time":789000,"text":"These are the two main"},{"time":792000,"text":"sort of binary oppositions within the logic of copyright law."},{"time":795000,"text":"It is more complex than this, but this will do."},{"time":798000,"text":"First: Is something an artistic object?"},{"time":801000,"text":"Then it deserves protection."},{"time":803000,"text":"Is it a utilitarian object?"},{"time":805000,"text":"Then no, it does not deserve protection."},{"time":807000,"text":"This is a difficult, unstable binary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":810000,"text":"The other one is: Is it an idea?"},{"time":813000,"text":"Is it something that needs to"},{"time":815000,"text":"freely circulate in a free society?"},{"time":817000,"text":"No protection."},{"time":819000,"text":"Or is it a physically fixed"},{"time":821000,"text":"expression of an idea:"},{"time":823000,"text":"something that somebody made"},{"time":825000,"text":"and they deserve to own it for a while and make money from it?"},{"time":828000,"text":"The problem is that digital technology"},{"time":830000,"text":"has completely subverted the logic"},{"time":832000,"text":"of this physically fixed, expression"},{"time":834000,"text":"versus idea concept."},{"time":837000,"text":"Nowadays,"},{"time":839000,"text":"we don't really recognize a book"},{"time":841000,"text":"as something that sits on our shelf"},{"time":843000,"text":"or music as something that is"},{"time":845000,"text":"a physical object that we can hold."},{"time":847000,"text":"It's a digital file."},{"time":849000,"text":"It is barely tethered to any sort of"},{"time":851000,"text":"physical reality in our minds."},{"time":853000,"text":"And these things, because we can copy and transmit them so easily,"},{"time":856000,"text":"actually circulate within our culture"},{"time":859000,"text":"a lot more like ideas"},{"time":861000,"text":"than like physically instantiated objects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":864000,"text":"Now, the conceptual issues are truly profound"},{"time":867000,"text":"when you talk about creativity"},{"time":869000,"text":"and ownership"},{"time":871000,"text":"and, let me tell you, we don't want to leave this just to lawyers to figure out."},{"time":874000,"text":"They're smart."},{"time":876000,"text":"I'm with one. He's my boyfriend, he's okay."},{"time":879000,"text":"He's smart, he's smart."},{"time":881000,"text":"But you want an interdisciplinary team of people"},{"time":883000,"text":"hashing this out,"},{"time":885000,"text":"trying to figure out: What is the kind of ownership model,"},{"time":888000,"text":"in a digital world,"},{"time":890000,"text":"that's going to lead to the most innovation?"},{"time":892000,"text":"And my suggestion is that"},{"time":894000,"text":"fashion might be a really good place"},{"time":896000,"text":"to start looking for a model"},{"time":898000,"text":"for creative industries in the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":901000,"text":"If you want more information about this research project,"},{"time":904000,"text":"please visit our website: it's ReadyToShare.org."},{"time":908000,"text":"And I really want to thank Veronica Jauriqui"},{"time":910000,"text":"for making this very fashionable presentation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":912000,"text":"Thank you so much. (Applause)"}]}]}